{"tid":365192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【流感肆虐】黨報文章引述專家　籲抵抗力差者暫緩遊香港","createTime":"2017-08-19T04:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T15:48:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"049f58de391c32ec7ca20be1f30e97b5a43adfb5","tid":365192,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170819/s00004/b579e531c7e6304e7ebfeaa7bfe600c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170819%2Fs00004%2Fb579e531c7e6304e7ebfeaa7bfe600c8.jpg&h=9cedaea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港夏季流感持續，中共黨媒《人民日報》海外版一篇署名文章引述專家建議，「抵抗力較差者，患病機會較大，最好暫緩去香港旅遊」。<br />\n<br />\n文章題為＜病毒變異是香港流感肆虐的罪魁嗎？＞，提到此次流感造成的死亡人數，已超過2003年SARS(嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症)直接導致的死亡人數，須分析為何流感病毒能肆虐香港，並造成如此多患者死亡。<br />\n<br />\n文章之後引述北京大學第一醫院感染疾病科副主任醫生徐京杭表示，與往年夏季流感比較，此次流感「疫情」出現更早，患者數量更多，「但從病原學來看，都是甲型流感H3為主」。他指出，病死者主要為65歲及以上老人，主要因為老人和小孩免疫力相對差，屬流感高危人群，又稱「流感本身不可怕，可怕的是併發症」。<br />\n<br />\n徐京杭續說，「現在尚無治療流感的特效藥，抗生素不能預防或治療流感，一些抗病毒藥也只能部分緩解症狀」，強調「接種疫苗是目前的預防方式」。他又指老年人或幼兒等「抵抗力較差者，患病機會較大，最好暫緩到香港旅遊」。<br />\n<br />\n（人民日報海外版）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170819/s00004/1503112653511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170819%2Fs00004%2F1503112653511&d=pd192AC71BAY2SsadnjqEdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=66cabddd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170819%2Fs00004%2F1503112653511&h=c59392cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170819/s00004/1503112653511</a>"},{"pid":"2b189aac1c7216ab86104502ad1f991ce7f445b1","tid":365192,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"想經濟懲罰香港呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4148c7d716f9667284ceb198f9172dd9d04785d2","tid":365192,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"唔好嚟最好"},{"pid":"b0f22d31597f100b544bd28aad55a3de07f4de44","tid":365192,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"唔想大陸人睇到香港人聲援泛民"},{"pid":"a93f620483b9cd9d3d30277a1422aee0297e1d43","tid":365192,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:48:16.000Z","msg":"可惜大陸人連毒霧都頂到 區區流感對佢地無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00dc50325fe058e109e5401e1fc5ab24bec4a0e","tid":365192,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"快d走啦 黎香港好易病㗎"}]}